      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just a metaphor. we aren't goblins, and there's no \"art\" in suffering through a meaningless cycle. if the end result is always zero, then any value we try to create is just a lie we tell ourselves to keep going. it feels more honest to just stop fighting it and accept the void instead of pretending there's some point to the struggle.",
